  <brief_title>Study of Safety and Efficacy of BCL201 and Idelalisib in Patients With FL and MCL</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase Ib Dose Escalation Study of BCL201 in Combination With Idelalisib in Patients With Follicular Lymphoma (FL) and Mantle Cell Lymphoma (MCL)</official_title>
